cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with image restoration and super-resolution. The use of deep learning also suggests that it could belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) categories. The mention of contextual information and multi-scale learning could also suggest Multimedia (cs.MM) as a possible category. Finally, the use of a deep network and the mention of improving performance could suggest Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) as another possible category.
